                     <interp inst="t18160918-56-person486" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . My watch had a blue ribbon to it.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18160918-56-person487">
                  WILLIAM 
                  BAKER
               <interp inst="t18160918-56-person487" type="surname" value="BAKER"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18160918-56-person487" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18160918-56-person487" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I can positively inform the Court that Mr. Edwards had the watch eight minutes before three that afternoon.</p>
